="300px" class="img-hero-ios"/><img class="img-hero-android" src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/634dc4f200ca7c1935e6237f_6.png" width="290" height="550" alt="" sizes="290px" data-w-id="194bdb4d-3faa-5238-6682-ba6995c2f0bc" loading="lazy" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/634dc4f200ca7c1935e6237f_6-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/634dc4f200ca7c1935e6237f_6-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/634dc4f200ca7c1935e6237f_6-p-1080.png 1080w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/634dc4f200ca7c1935e6237f_6.png 2105w"/></div><div data-w-id="11165365-4466-7a19-fa77-56126905b4bd" style="opacity:0" class="logos-store"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61bb2061971cd56236723200_badge_apple_store.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61bb20652a29eb28155bb0e0_badge_google_store.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></div></div><div class="circle-hero-bg"></div></section><section data-w-id="76dc57a8-c9f0-b437-3fdf-f23a405edb0a" class="section-feature"><div class="container w-container"><div class="col-feature w-row"><div class="w-col w-col-6 w-col-stack"><div class="block-feature-intro"><h4 data-w-id="9be36e59-b674-4ee8-41d6-a95569f2913b" style="opacity:0"><strong class="bold-text-2">Have you ever gone to a wedding only to discover you’ve left your gift at home? Has your gift list gotten so long and overwhelming you just don’t know where to start?<br/></strong></h4><p data-w-id="aef48f44-d2b0-f51b-2b90-173a3ac1bc22" style="opacity:0" class="paragraph-2"><br/>With Giftd, we make the process to send and receive monetary gifts easy and meaningful. No more writing checks or running to the ATM to pull out cash.<br/> <br/>Now you can send and receive custom, beautifully designed greeting cards online and attach any amount you like.</p></div></div><div class="w-col w-col-6 w-col-stack"><div class="w-layout-grid grid-feature"><div data-w-id="5cdbc0e3-7b76-3ceb-4c4e-bf0fe188a7e5" style="opacity:0"><figure class="icon-feautre"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61c20eba4fe0a00e8f78e67d_calendar.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></figure><h4 class="heading">Create your own event</h4><p class="text-small">Create an event and invite your guests so they can send your presents with one click.</p></div><div data-w-id="311f584b-0578-60fa-b423-3001ac8ffe04" style="opacity:0"><figure class="icon-feautre"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61c20ec1bde290aed9f56ead_gift.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></figure><h4 class="heading-2">Gifts simplified</h4><p class="text-small">Simple as just choosing an amount and setting your personalized message. No more last minute stops to buy a card!</p></div><div data-w-id="3a10a01f-ea79-2e66-9ea7-2577fd7c784b" style="opacity:0"><figure class="icon-feautre"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61c20f13c5ff380bce5ba05a_flash.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></figure><h4 class="heading-3">Fast and efficient</h4><p class="text-small">All the money gifted goes straight to the recipients account. No need to set any extra steps.</p></div><div data-w-id="eb616dfc-70a8-be04-2ffc-c9cb12e8afef" style="opacity:0"><figure class="icon-feautre"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61c20f1cfdd84f5b01ec1435_heart.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></figure><h4 class="heading-4">Get back</h4><p class="text-small">Your friends can also send gifts your way. All your contacts automatically get saved for future events.</p></div></div></div></div></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61bb4c65c552e488485b48b7_bg_circle.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="bg-circle"/></section><section class="section-form"><div class="container w-container"><div class="block-get-access"><div class="block-get-access-inner"><h2 class="color-white">Get beta access</h2><p class="color-white">Subscribe to be a part of our early beta.</p><div class="w-form"><form id="email-form" name="email-form" data-name="Email Form" method="get" class="form-get-access" data-wf-page-id="61ba070daaed59174d0cd0e5" data-wf-element-id="d6854cbb-263b-6a3b-19ae-6d77b44e3883"><input type="email" class="text-field w-input" maxlength="256" name="email" data-name="Email" placeholder="Enter your email" id="email" required=""/><input type="submit" value="Invite" data-wait="Please wait..." class="button button-form w-button"/></form><div class="w-form-done"><div>Thank you! Your submission has been received!</div></div><div class="w-form-fail"><div>Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.</div></div></div></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/61bb83b1e8d2c8b2f850678e_img_gift.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="img-gift"/></div></div></section><footer id="footer" class="footer"><div class="w-container"><div class="text-block-3">Copyright © 2023 Giftd LLC. All rights reserved.</div></div></footer><script src="https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/61ba070daaed599ef00cd0e4/js/webflow.402c9f265.js" type="text/javascript"></script></body></html>
